train to New York.

14:33.209 --> 14:34.667
No, we'll rent a car.

14:34.751 --> 14:36.000
They... They don't
leave without you,

14:36.083 --> 14:37.876
and they don't get
diverted to Boston.

14:37.959 --> 14:40.209
Okay. Okay, sweetie,
whatever.

14:40.292 --> 14:41.417
I'll meet you...
Five minutes.

