where the ladies' room is?

15:28.167 --> 15:29.584
You mean
the men's room.

15:29.667 --> 15:30.918
No, I don't need
the men's room,
I need the ladies' room.

15:31.000 --> 15:32.751
Over there.
Ohh!

15:32.834 --> 15:35.167
Nancy? Nancy,
we can still
make the train.

15:35.250 --> 15:36.918
We can still... Uhh.

15:37.000 --> 15:38.792
Excuse me,
can you go in there
and get my wife, please?

15:38.876 --> 15:41.000
It's an emergency.
She's wearing a brown coat,

15:41.083 --> 15:42.876
she has a blue dress,
uh, blonde hair,

15:42.959 --> 15:44.751
and... Just thanks, thanks.

15:44.834 --> 15:46.375
Henry, I got lost.

15:46.459 --> 15:47.792
Nancy, we can still
make the train.

15:47.876 --> 15:49.584
Come on, come on, come on.
Henry, I have to go...

15:49.667 --> 15:51.542
No, no, we don't have time.
It leaves in two minutes.

15:51.626 --> 15:52.834
The train's still here?

15:53.751 --> 15:55.500
She didn't want
to come out!

15:58.751 --> 16:00.500
This way, this way, this way!
Come on, come on!

16:00.584 --> 16:01.626
Okay.

16:04.292 --> 16:05.500
I'll run on ahead.

16:05.584 --> 16:08.292
Run ahead of me.
I can't in these heels.

16:09.459 --> 16:11.292
