Oh, my God!

16:12.167 --> 16:13.292
Hold it!

16:13.375 --> 16:15.500
Hold it! Okay.

16:15.584 --> 16:16.959
Oh, it's here.

16:17.709 --> 16:18.959
All right. Okay.

16:19.959 --> 16:21.667
Oh, on a full bladder,
I made it.

16:21.751 --> 16:23.250
Oh, I forgive you
the peanut butter.

16:23.334 --> 16:24.500
Okay. Come on,
I'm exhausted.

16:24.584 --> 16:25.918
Let's see if
we can get a seat.

16:26.584 --> 16:27.626
Ohh.
Ohh.

16:28.542 --> 16:29.667
Oh.

16:30.542 --> 16:31.876
Excuse me,

16:31.959 --> 16:33.542
is this the 3:38
to New York?

16:33.626 --> 16:35.542
No, that is.

16:37.667 --> 16:39.334
(TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWS)

16:40.542 --> 16:41.542
Oh.

16:44.375 --> 16:46.292
Hertz, nothing, Avis,
nothing, budget, nothing.

16:46.375 --> 16:47.626
We've gotta find a car.

16:47.709 --> 16:49.209
I know. We have
to be nice, Henry.

16:49.292 --> 16:50.667
We have to be nice.
Gotta be nice.

16:50.751 --> 16:52.500
Yeah. The guy at Avis
didn't like you very much.

16:52.584 --> 16:54.000
We were both
in a bad mood.
Be nice.

16:54.083 --> 16:55.209
Hi, can I help you folks?

16:55.292 --> 16:56.751
Well, yes, but first,
how are you?

16:56.834 --> 16:59.292
Fine.
Great. Well, we'd
like to rent a car.

16:59.375 --> 17:00.918
Great. Compact,
midsize, or luxury?

17:01.000 --> 17:03.584
Ah, compacted.

17:03.667 --> 17:04.626
Okay.

17:05.542 --> 17:07.292
Oh, actually, we're
all out of compacts.

17:07.375 --> 17:09.751
Oh, midsize
would be fine.

17:09.834 --> 17:11.250
Okay.

17:11.334 --> 17:12.876
Oops, actually,

17:12.959 --> 17:14.584
we don't have any
midsized vehicles either.

17:14.667 --> 17:15.792
All we have is
one luxury sedan.

17:16.542 --> 17:17.751
Huh.

17:17.834 --> 17:19.500
Well, I'm not sure
why you asked, then,

17:19.584 --> 17:21.542
what car we...
We'll take
a luxury sedan.

17:22.751 --> 17:24.417
Okay.
Sounds good.

17:26.000 --> 17:27.876
You know, honey,
they should really
change this sign

17:27.959 --> 17:29.459
to "we have car."

17:30.667 --> 17:32.000
If I could have
your credit card?

17:32.083 --> 17:33.375
Absolutely.

17:33.459 --> 17:35.083
I think you'll
enjoy the car, sir.

17:35.167 --> 17:37.584
It's totally
state-of-the-art.
Practically drives itself.

17:37.667 --> 17:39.250
Would you like the
collision insurance?

17:39.334 --> 17:41.375
Well, if the car
drives itself and
we have an accident,

17:41.459 --> 17:43.792
then it would be
the car's fault, right?

