40:04.751 --> 40:06.918
Well... Um...

40:07.000 --> 40:08.876
I'd like to get some food.
I'm hungry.

40:08.959 --> 40:11.459
And, you know, uh...
We don't have any bags.

40:11.542 --> 40:12.667
