44:52.417 --> 44:53.751
Yes.

44:53.834 --> 44:55.959
So, Greg...
Mmm?

44:56.042 --> 44:58.584
Is what I think's gonna
happen gonna happen?

44:58.667 --> 45:00.125
Mmm? 'Cause if it is,

45:00.209 --> 45:02.250
