45:37.918 --> 45:39.834
(CHUCKLES)
Mrs. Robinson.

45:39.918 --> 45:42.167
Mrs. Robinson. That's sexy.

45:42.250 --> 45:43.334
Hey.

45:43.417 --> 45:45.125
Nice to meet you,
Mrs. Robinson.

45:45.584 --> 45:47.083
See you later.

45:54.500 --> 45:57.250
We'll have the lobster,
the grilled salmon,

45:57.334 --> 45:59.584
and the creme brûlée,
please.

45:59.667 --> 46:01.834
And could you throw in
a couple of steaks?

46:01.918 --> 46:03.334
No dressing
on the salad,

46:03.417 --> 46:05.042
and we need this
as soon as possible.

46:05.125 --> 46:07.083
Thank you very much.
Bye-bye.

46:07.167 --> 46:09.125
You were really something
at the bar tonight.

46:09.209 --> 46:11.167
Oh, Henry, we are
going to have

46:11.250 --> 46:13.167
