47:01.000 --> 47:02.167
Mrs. Robinson.

47:02.250 --> 47:04.042
Cut it...
Can you see me?

47:04.125 --> 47:05.626
Yes, I... Shh!

47:05.709 --> 47:07.000
Pull me out. I'm stuck.

47:07.083 --> 47:08.542
30 seconds!

47:08.626 --> 47:10.584
Uh! Uh! Uh!

47:12.834 --> 47:14.667
Okay. All right.

47:14.751 --> 47:16.292
All right.
All right.

47:16.375 --> 47:18.500
Don't you let him...
You know, and...

47:18.584 --> 47:20.334
And whatever you...
