47:20.417 --> 47:22.834
Honey, I won't!
Just shut up!

47:24.834 --> 47:26.292
Hi.
Hi.

47:27.375 --> 47:29.000
I was wondering
if you'd still be here.

47:29.083 --> 47:30.918
Oh, well, why
wouldn't I be?

47:31.000 --> 47:32.918
I don't know.
Some women might find

47:33.000 --> 47:35.125
