48:23.959 --> 48:25.667
Well, you better bring
a fire extinguisher.

48:25.751 --> 48:27.167
Oh, Mrs. Robinson!

48:27.250 --> 48:29.000
Ohh! Oh, now,
don't start now.

48:29.083 --> 48:31.417
Don't start now.
