begs to be let inside.

50:20.876 --> 50:23.083
I'm not the type of guy
that's gonna
turn someone away.

50:23.167 --> 50:24.709
Ohh... Ohhh!

50:24.792 --> 50:25.834
Nancy!

50:25.918 --> 50:27.876
Uhh! Aah! Ohh!

50:27.959 --> 50:29.876
Ohh!

50:39.709 --> 50:42.500
Nancy, I'm gonna have you
checked for testicles.

50:42.584 --> 50:45.500
